\">[mongodb-org-3.4]</span></div>\n</div><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`name=MongoDB Repository`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token constant\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>MongoDB Repository</span></div>\n</div><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`baseurl=https://repo.mongodb.org/yum/redhat/$releasever/mongodb-org/3.4/x86_64/`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token constant\">baseurl</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>https://repo.mongodb.org/yum/redhat/$releasever/mongodb-org/3.4/x86_64/</span></div>\n</div><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`gpgcheck=1`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token constant\">gpgcheck</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>1</span></div>\n</div><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`enabled=1`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token constant\">enabled</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>1</span></div>\n</div><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`gpgkey=https://www.mongodb.org/static/pgp/server-3.4.asc`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token constant\">gpgkey</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span>https://www.mongodb.org/static/pgp/server-3.4.asc</span></div>\n</div></code></pre>\n    </div>\n<p>Following that, you can install the mongodb-org package with this command:</p>\n<div class='gatsby-highlight'>\n      <pre class='language-bash'><code><div class='line-wrapper'>\n<div class='copy-button' title='Copy' onClick='copyToClipboard(`sudo yum install mongodb-org`)'></div>\n<div><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> yum <span class=\"token function\">install</span> mongodb-org</div>\n</div></code></pre>\